    "body": "``` CoffeeScript\nsearchBoxWidget = instantsearch.widgets.searchBox(\n    container: '.app-search'\n    wrapInput: true\n    autofocus: true\n    cssClasses:\n        root: 'input-group'\n        input: 'form-control'\n)\n```\n\nJust noticed that problem also occurs with root class. Other widgets css classes works fine.\n",
